| GET | `/api/projects` | All open projects from DB |
| POST | `/api/projects` | Create project (client) |
| POST | `/api/apply` | Freelancer applies → `applications` table |
| GET | `/api/applications?project_id=X` | Client views applications for project |
| POST | `/api/hire` | Client hires → update application + project |
| GET | `/api/freelancer/projects?freelancer_id=X` | Freelancer sees assigned projects |
| GET | `/api/stats/dashboard/:userId` | Dashboard stats |
| OPTIONS | `/api/<path>` | CORS preflight |

All responses include `Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *`.

